Package: spiralize
Type: Package
Title: Visualize Data on Spirals
Version: 0.99.0
Date: 2021-06-09
Author: Zuguang Gu
Maintainer: Zuguang Gu <z.gu@dkfz.de>
Depends: R (>= 3.6.0), grid
Imports: GlobalOptions (>= 0.1.1), 
         GetoptLong (>= 0.1.8), 
         circlize,
         stats,
         methods,
         grDevices,
         ComplexHeatmap,
         lubridate
Suggests: knitr, 
          rmarkdown,
          grImport,
          grImport2,
          jpeg,
          png,
          tiff,
          ape,
          cranlogs,
          cowplot,
          dendextend
Description: The package visualizes data along an Archimedean spiral. 
    It has two major advantages for visualization: 1. to visualize data with very long axis,
    and 2. to visualize periodic data.
VignetteBuilder: knitr
URL: https://github.com/jokergoo/spiral
